<TR><TD BGCOLOR=#d0d0ff><FONT FACE="Helvetica" SIZE=-1>
Welcome and thank you for trusting  Cronosii,  the E-mail
suite we designed for you.</P>

<P>Cronos II comes  with a number of features that make it a very good choice for your E-mail tasks on almost any platform; <B>GNU/Linux</B>, <B>GNU/HURD</B>,
<B>Unix</B>,
<B>FreeBSD</B>, <B>Mac-OSX</B>,
<B>Microsoft Windows</B>, etc.</P>

<P>Cronos II @VERSION@ comes with the following features:

<UL>
<LI>HTML support;</li>
<LI>attachments support;</li>
<LI>IMAP support;</li>
<LI>POP support;</li>
<LI>APOP support;</li>
<LI>Spool support;</li>
<LI>Filters support;</li>
<LI>Multiples identities and accounts support;</li>
<LI>Highly GNOME integrated interface;</li>
<LI>Interface editable through <B>Glade</B>.
</UL>

<P>Only you really know what <em>your needs</em> are;
so if you have some other need from Cronos II, be sure
to contact us, (that's <B>another feature of Cronos II</B>: Open minded programmers.)

